snippet.title: Prose & Codes - A Game of Literary Ciphers (2022 Steam + Itch.io)
snippet.description:
STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1718910/Prose__Codes/
ITCH.IO: https://herogameco.itch.io/proseandcodes

Explore the wonderful world of books through deceptively simple ciphers. A portion of every sale will go to Project Gutenberg, an online library of over 60,000 free ebooks.
